item.title: How can I make a barrows in 317?
item.dc:creator: @andy_d_b34st andy d b34st
item.description:
@andy_d_b34st wrote:

Well it shouldn’t really matter what base unless you basically want to spoon feed him. He just has to add in cases and whatnot so when he digs, it brings him to sarcopagus(?), if he kills the brother, it tele’s him to the next sarcopagus, and make it so the last brother that gets sent to is the one that has drops. Isn’t all that hard, but can take a little bit of time finding the proper locations for these things.
